{"id":136657,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/02/简讯：科学家警告大鱼将从海中消失/","date":"2011-02-19T13:30:16Z","modified":"2011-02-19T13:30:16Z","title":"简讯：科学家警告大鱼将从海中消失","content":"<div>\n<p>海洋科学专家警告说，继续过度捕捞将使诸如鱈魚、比目鱼和鲨鱼等大型掠食性鱼类在本世纪中从海洋中彻底消失。</p>\n<p>研究人员对美国科学促进会表示，大型掠食性鱼类数量急剧减少导致小型摄食鱼类诸如沙丁鱼和凤尾鱼的数量在过去一个世纪当中增加了一倍。</p>\n<p>专家警告这有可能在生物多样性以及人类食品消费方面导致灾难性后果，另外气候变化因素会使问题更加严重。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/j8LS2mnC1R97ipFU7eB229U0wKQ/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/j8LS2mnC1R97ipFU7eB229U0wKQ/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/j8LS2mnC1R97ipFU7eB229U0wKQ/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/j8LS2mnC1R97ipFU7eB229U0wKQ/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=u7DC1MepoNY:sXHT1nA0ccA:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=u7DC1MepoNY:sXHT1nA0ccA:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=u7DC1MepoNY:sXHT1nA0ccA:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=u7DC1MepoNY:sXHT1nA0ccA:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=u7DC1MepoNY:sXHT1nA0ccA:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=u7DC1MepoNY:sXHT1nA0ccA:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/u7DC1MepoNY\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>需翻墙软件请发电邮(最好用Gmail)到:gongminshehui1ATg